Package: miEdgeR
Type: Package
Title: Mutual Information Network and Hypergraph Analysis for Seurat Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Elhadi", 
           family = "Iich", 
           email = "iichelhadi@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for mutual information-based gene network analysis,
    hypergraph construction, and pseudotime-aware analyses for single-cell RNA-seq data.
Depends: R (>= 4.0), Seurat, igraph, dplyr, ggplot2, clusterProfiler, org.Hs.eg.db, ggpubr, ggVennDiagram, pheatmap
Imports: Seurat, igraph, clusterProfiler, org.Hs.eg.db, dplyr, ggplot2, ggraph, flextable, pheatmap, RColorBrewer, DOSE, ReactomePA, ggpubr, scales, grDevices
